nodes.text: The Wannschok Tenements was a section of the Nikto Sector on the moon Nar Shaddaa that was named after the Wannschok, a famous desert on the planet Kintan. Sawtooth Salvage and the Alien Arms Bazaar were located in the area, as was the recruitment center for the Power Guard Project, and the Kintan Kings gang controlled the area as they did the entire Nikto Sector.
